{"tid":1909522,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"到底日本人係點發音？？？","createTime":"2020-03-04T04:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T08:47:50.000Z","uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"47d5b5293ac99d3cd1ae08cce790d1d8564173a6","tid":1909522,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:29:35.000Z","msg":"其實日本人到底係點發音？ <br />\n<br />\n特別係　つ　ず　じ　呢3個。其實我所有音都發到，但就係呢3個點都無日本味<br />\n<br />\n睇好多網上youtuber, 比如大j 周庭 甚至咩講日文的女生tiffany, 都唔係好講到果種日本味<br />\n<br />\n之前自己睇左一個日本人教改善發音<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AV4P_G7L7ho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAV4P_G7L7ho&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeISwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=322bf125\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AV4P_G7L7ho</a><br />\n<br />\n其實都有進步<br />\n<br />\n但一到 続ける　ずつ　傷つく　呢d 一讀得快就走樣<br />\n<br />\n呢度既巴打有無tips?<br />\n<br />\nbtw 見到youtube有個23歲先去日本既鬼佬講到好似日本人咁，但佢既し音都係有口音。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SU4oPlbs5c0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSU4oPlbs5c0&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeISwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=855472d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SU4oPlbs5c0</a><br />\n<br />\n其實係味調返轉唔好咁在意口音"},{"pid":"722406adf373618d2f6c5e51994848f1c776afa9","tid":1909522,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f454ac2242d2316123c77d2cd536bdba7d226dab","tid":1909522,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"ず舌尖掂住下方門牙<br />\nつ掂上方<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe7eeb72de9f36f102835be5521c4c19b481d63","tid":1909522,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"你中文讀個「嗚」字個u音係圓嘴<br />\n你試下扁嘴咁讀個「う」<br />\n「嗚」同「う」嘅分別好似「衣」同「於」咁 一個圓嘴 一個扁嘴<br />\n「つ」都係扁嘴"},{"pid":"a5041e2176c99b2dfc92a2ee5825bae189ee661e","tid":1909522,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":